				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Pet /shield only works for pets with the same name as their owner.  So it currently works for beastlord pets, Host of the Elements, Shaman AA, Necro wake the dead for examples...
<br />

<br />
There was a point a long time ago when PoP first came out that worked for all pets but that was changed quickly.
<br />

<br />

<br />
~Tukodo</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
