			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-weight: bold">Shared Health </span>
<br />
Level 65 
<br />
3 / 6 / 9 / 12 / 15 
<br />
Cast Time: Instant 
<br />
Recast Time: 15 Minutes 
<br />
Gives Magician pets the ability to /shield their master for 12 seconds per rank, up to 1 minute. 
<br />
Once this ability is activated, pets will /shield their master from incoming damage, effectively cutting incoming damage to the mage in half with the pet taking 50% to 75% of the damage intended for the magician. <span style="font-weight: bold">Each rank adds 12 seconds to this ability. </span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
